U.S. Treasury Department Schedule for Monday, Aug. 1

-- B y   V i n c e n t   D e l   G i u d i c e
-- 
2011-08-01T12:13:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-01/u-s-treasury-department-schedule-for-monday-aug-1.html
The following is a reformatted
version of the U.S. Treasury Department’s daily release on the
schedule for Secretary Timothy F. Geithner and other officials:  On Monday, at 3 p.m., Treasury will release its current
estimates of marketable borrowing in advance of the Treasury
Borrowing Advisory Committee (TBAC) meeting on Tuesday.
Additional financing details relating to Treasury’s Quarterly
Refunding will be released at 10 a.m. on Wednesday, Aug. 3.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vincent Del Giudice in  Washington  
 vdelgiudice@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Wellisz at   cwellisz@bloomberg.net  